import { Box, Container, Grid, Paper, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import { withStyles } from '@mui/styles'
import React from 'react'

const styles = withStyles(()=>({
    mainGridClass:{
        backgroundColor:'green'
    }
}))


export default function ProfileComponent() {
    const useStyle = styles();
  return (
    <>  <Paper>
        <Container>
        <Grid className={useStyle.mainGridClass}>
            <Box>
                <Typography>Click here to view Profile</Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box>
                <Typography>Click here to view Education</Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box>
                <Typography>Click here to view Experience</Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box>
                <Typography>Click here to view Skills</Typography>
            </Box>
            </Grid></Container>
        </Paper>
    </>
  )
}
